WEBVTT

00:00.372 --> 00:01.799
Previously on "Heartland"...

00:01.800 --> 00:04.269
I just remember the
atmosphere back then.

00:04.303 --> 00:05.719
If you really do miss it,
maybe you should come with me

00:05.739 --> 00:07.505
on my rodeo tour.

00:07.896 --> 00:09.307
There's nothing like it.

00:09.341 --> 00:12.932
Is there any way you'd ever
consider hiring me again?

00:12.952 --> 00:15.813
Welcome back.

00:15.847 --> 00:17.698
Well, I just got
my old job back.

00:17.718 --> 00:19.884
That's great.

00:20.215 --> 00:23.334
- I should get going.
- Ty?

00:24.093 --> 00:25.656
I miss you.

00:26.234 --> 00:28.047
Take care of yourself.

00:30.000 --> 00:36.074
